{"tid":1745061,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動改進】有份黎明晨曦乜乜乜行動既手足同我入黎","createTime":"2019-11-22T04:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T05:37:19.000Z","uid":254110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"09f8f55030b1e712d724c4f8065cab8b65673251","tid":1745061,"uid":254110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:45:11.000Z","msg":"其實你地知唔知依個行動既目的係咩<br />\n係令到D港豬<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被罷工</span></span><br />\n令佢地返唔到工唔係塞係返緊工條路<br />\n你塞佢地返工果條路只係令佢地遲左半個至一個鐘返到公司<br />\n港豬既心態係：屌都出左黎等多陣先啦<br />\n<br />\n如果塞佢地出門口條路就唔同<br />\n起碼有一部分人唔會同公司哂時間<br />\n直接打返去話冇車返<br />\n<br />\n好啦今個星期黎明已經完哂<br />\n唔該依兩日討論下有咩地方可以改進<br />\n好似上星期咁成功"},{"pid":"f36c1b653cdb91a13db6edcd6541b994fda30aad","tid":1745061,"uid":254110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:46:56.000Z","msg":"塞隧道口堅有用<br />\n有冇辦法令其他隧道都好似紅隧咁"},{"pid":"4d43e98deb3a4318e5a08023702412da3ddc7efe","tid":1745061,"uid":254110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:57:35.000Z","msg":"一直重複做同一樣野唔係叫be water"},{"pid":"4d3509e02774e41a72d0fd070c798ab082947b35","tid":1745061,"uid":254110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:00:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以幫手推"},{"pid":"a3ed0ecd5acff8d6e3ab7fc6a6af92ad1d3635a3","tid":1745061,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:37:09.000Z","msg":"1土"},{"pid":"c299383f93ab3550842e919e7dff17efe3f8675e","tid":1745061,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:37:19.000Z","msg":"推"}]}